com.philemonworks.selfdiagnose

Class DiagnosticTaskResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.philemonworks.selfdiagnose.DiagnosticTaskResult
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CompositeDiagnosticTaskResult

    public class DiagnosticTaskResult
extends Object
    DiagnosticTaskResult hold information about the execution of a DiagnosticTask and known how to create a report for logging.
    • Passed means: task completed succesfully
    • Failed means: execution task succes but tests failed
    • Error means: execution task failed (because of Exception)
    • Unknown means: result is not set and therefore not reported
    Author:
    emicklei
